      "MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|6851,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|5521,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|9524,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|327361,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|191831",
